name: Entanglements.00
description:
Tangle the reality. 
.
Allow your camera and show your hand a few seconds to interact.
..
Control tentacles with your hand which will be detected with your camera.
...
Move your hand horizontally to change direction of tentacles, vertically to change magnitude of the vectors.
....
A machine learning model is used for detection.
.....
Made with p5js & mediapipe.
......
Artist: Kerem Altaylar
